Subject: Re: Mechanical Ventilation certification - 55A Parriwi Rd, Mosman NSW 2088

 

Hi Felix

 

Thankyou for getting in touch.

 

Yes we need a performance solution for the existing cinema room at Mosman.  We need BOTH light and ventilation addressed. 

 

We do not want to add a window as the building is finished and the cinema room does not want natural light.  There is a good mechanical ventilation / AC system in place now.

 

See plans attached and Firas BCA report.  Council notes:

 

2. Submission of a BCA report to address how the Cinema room achieves compliance with Part 3.8.4 (light) and Part 3.8.5 (ventilation) now that the existing windows have been removed. In this regard all habitable rooms are required to achieve minimum light and ventilation requirements, including cinema/theatre rooms. 
The BCA report prepared by Silver End Pty Ltd, Issue A, Dated 24 June 2022 fails to address these requirements of the BCA. 

 

Call me if you need – Can you pls provide a quote today?

 

Emili
